<html><head><title>Monk feign death improved</title></head><body class="newsbody" ><div class=newbody><h2>EverQuest Vault -- EQ </h3><h3>Monk feign death improved</h3><p>Eric "Grumbuk" Cosky, the Assistant Lead Programmer for EQ posted a note on EQ Live concerning Monk's feign death skill.  Here's the whole post:<blockquote>Just wanted to let you folks know that today along with other code changes that went to Test server tonight we also improved the monk feign death success rate. It was previously capped at 95% at 100 skill and now it ramps up the success rate for higher skill levels. I'll leave it to the parsers to figure out the final cap </blockquote>Less waiting on dead monks when raiding is always a good thing =).  If you want to read it for yourself you can do so <a href="http://eqforums.station.sony.com/eq/board/message?board.id=monkbalance&message.id=6653&no_redir=true#M6653">here</a>.</div><p><div classs=copyright><font face=arial size=2 color=#959595>News Story from EverQuest Vault -- EQ <br>News Date: Mon 13 Dec 2004<br>Link: http://eqvault.ign.com//index.php#4116<br>Printed On: Tue Dec 28 5:02:54 PST 2004<br>©2004 IGN Entertainment</font></span>